{"title":"致海上的石油勘探者","authors":["黎焕颐"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致海上的石油勘探者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎焕颐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海，无风三尺浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，真有翻云覆雨的龙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，是水的习性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜欢澎湃？喜欢激动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，也有人误会："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是风在暗地怂恿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，我终于明白："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来有地火在海底汹涌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好！你们给风平反了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以科学的无私。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理应记功！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普罗米修士从天庭窃火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为上所不容……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你们取火于海的深层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕不怕触怒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆万钧的天公？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我：水中取火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和火中取粟是否不同？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水中取火的英雄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历来水火不相容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，你们却无所畏惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦然来往于水深火热之中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是从那儿得来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大仁、大智、大勇？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美呵，燧人氏的后裔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从当初的钻木取火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到如今的钻水取火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人从来就不窝囊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火种从来就没有中断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给华夏创造光明的传统……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍惜这传统吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我指的不是孔明用兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惯用火攻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我指的是数典忘祖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是当前世态的偏头痛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医疗的方法不妨借用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上勘探者取火的雄风……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说不是呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的医术"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用火疗，历来别有一工……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}